Control + D - find the file in big project
Turn on Pin up  or Check Options -> Environment -> Tabs and Windows -> Show pinned tabs in separate row or single clieck file ( wont create new tab )
Ctronl K  ControlE - clean up code   ( menu -> configure Code Clean up or Options-> TextEditor-> C# ->Code Style-> General )
Hold down Cursor - to write/delete muliple lines  // control+ D -> copy lines faster
Options-> Projects and Solutions -> Restore SOlution Explorer project hierarchy state on solution load
